NAME
    App::XLog - XLog Application

SYNOPSIS
        > cd content/dir
        > xlog init
        > xlog make
        > xlog start

STATUS
    This software is pre-alpha. Don't use it yet.

DESCRIPTION
    XLog lets you publish your public brain in a reusable way.

